desc_short	-----								Folk Tale is a single-player fantasy village builder ARPG game. If you enjoyed Warcraft 3, The Settlers, Banished, The Guild 2, Majesty 2 or Black and White 2, we hope you'll like Folk Tale. Village building, economy, heroes, combat and adventuring with both campaign and sandbox play.							
developer									Games Foundry								
